1	9	4	Scaling AI & Patient Experience for Weave's Healthcare Platform	<html>\n    <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">\n        <p>Hello Taylor,</p>\n        \n        <p>I noticed <strong>Weave</strong> is expanding the team with roles like **Founding Ai Engineer** ΓÇö thatΓÇÖs exciting! Congratulations on your continued growth and investment in AI.</p>\n        <p>As you scale your innovative platform, ensuring your AI initiatives are built on robust data and that your patient experience remains seamless can become resource-intensive.</p>\n        \n        <p>With Weave's focus on a comprehensive customer experience and payments platform for small and medium-sized healthcare businesses, we see a clear fit, particularly in areas like:</p>\n        <ul>\n            <li><strong>Accelerating AI Development:</strong> Providing specialized data collection and precise data labeling for the unique healthcare scenarios your new AI features will address, ensuring high-quality training data for your Founding AI Engineer.</li>\n            <li><strong>Enhancing Patient Engagement:</strong> Offering human-in-the-loop support for complex patient interactions or filtering/qualifying leads that require nuanced human review, ensuring your AI-driven communication tools maintain empathy and accuracy.</li>\n        </ul>\n        \n        <p>Adept Technologies provides scalable support that delivers affordability, speed, and quality, allowing your team to focus on innovating your core platform and enhancing patient outcomes, while we handle the specialized data and human review tasks.</p>\n        \n        <p>Would you be open to a quick 15-minute chat this week to explore how we can specifically support <strong>Weave</strong>'s next phase of AI-driven growth and patient experience?</p>\n    </body>\n</html>	pending	2026-01-22 13:39:24.228729	\N	1
